      <title>哈马斯称以色列袭击导致领导人哈尼亚的三个儿子死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/hamas-says-israeli-strike-killed-three-sons-of-leader-haniyeh</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯激进组织称，以色列对加沙的空袭造成哈马斯领导人伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚的三个儿子死亡，这是自六个月前战争爆发以来最引人注目的伤亡事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/hamas-says-israeli-strike-killed-three-sons-of-leader-haniyeh</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:49:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟在六月选举前为新移民规则扫清道路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/eu-clears-way-for-new-immigration-rules-ahead-of-june-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟扫清了通过一项关键移民和庇护政策的重大障碍，一些人权活动人士和立法者批评该政策可能会加剧现有问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/eu-clears-way-for-new-immigration-rules-ahead-of-june-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:45:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>研究显示南非化石燃料补贴高达 60 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/south-africa-fossil-fuel-subsidies-top-6-billion-study-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据加拿大一家智库称，南非的化石燃料补贴在 2023 财年增至 1180 亿兰特（63 亿美元），提供了鼓励继续使用化石燃料的激励措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/south-africa-fossil-fuel-subsidies-top-6-billion-study-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:28:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>津巴布韦财政部长认为 ZiG 货币将结束市场波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/zimbabwe-s-finance-chief-sees-new-zig-currency-ending-stock-market-volatility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦财政部长 Mthuli Ncube 表示，津巴布韦新货币 ZiG 的推出预计将结束股市波动，并有助于恢复总体价格稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/zimbabwe-s-finance-chief-sees-new-zig-currency-ending-stock-market-volatility</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:15:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士支持欧盟对六名哈马斯支持者实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/switzerland-backs-eu-sanctions-against-six-hamas-supporters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士政府周三在一份声明中表示，瑞士正在对六名参与资助哈马斯和巴勒斯坦伊斯兰圣战组织的个人实施金融制裁和旅行限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/switzerland-backs-eu-sanctions-against-six-hamas-supporters</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:06:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>曾经被嘲笑的议长候选人汤姆·埃默（Tom Emmer）饰演迈克·约翰逊（Mike Johnson）摇摇欲坠，向特朗普示好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/trump-courted-by-once-scorned-speaker-hopeful-tom-emmer-as-mike-johnson-teeters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五个月前，唐纳德·特朗普在社交媒体上发了一条严厉的帖子，让汤姆·埃默成为众议院议长的希望破灭，这位前总统在海湖庄园的一场筹款活动上赞扬了他，为这位明尼苏达州国会议员赢得了超过 30 万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/trump-courted-by-once-scorned-speaker-hopeful-tom-emmer-as-mike-johnson-teeters</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西拒绝美国放弃乙醇进口关税的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/brazil-rebuffs-us-pressure-to-abandon-tariffs-on-ethanol-imports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[农业部长卡洛斯·法瓦罗表示，尽管拜登政府提出“严厉”抱怨，巴西仍将维持对美国乙醇进口的关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/brazil-rebuffs-us-pressure-to-abandon-tariffs-on-ethanol-imports</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 14:54:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士宣布六月中旬举行乌克兰和平峰会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/switzerland-announces-summit-on-ukraine-peace-plan-on-june-15-16</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士将于6月15日至16日主办一次高级别会议，以巩固全球对乌克兰倡导的和平框架的支持，该框架将结束与俄罗斯的战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/switzerland-announces-summit-on-ukraine-peace-plan-on-june-15-16</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 13:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷克废除分拆计划，东欧最大公用事业公司获得救济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/east-eu-s-top-utility-gets-some-relief-as-czechs-drop-split-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克立法者放弃了一项旨在帮助政府改造占主导地位的电力公司CEZ AS的提案，结束了与投资者长达一年的争执，投资者对股价造成压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/east-eu-s-top-utility-gets-some-relief-as-czechs-drop-split-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 10:41:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非民意调查显示，祖玛党人数激增，非国大支持率下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/anc-support-plunges-in-south-african-poll-as-zuma-party-surges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新的民意调查显示，南非执政党非洲人国民大会的支持率正在大幅下降，前总统雅各布·祖马支持的政党可能会在下个月的选举后成为该国第三大政党。兰特走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/anc-support-plunges-in-south-african-poll-as-zuma-party-surges</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 08:13:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
